===Sonarkhettir Franciscan Firgozecho kalea fatracho Khuris===
Poile Igroz bandche adim, Franciscan Missionarani Siole ani Assagao modem Sonarkhett mhonlolea dongrar Mae De Deus Igorz bandli. Ti mode bandleli ani novea Christaum zalelea Anjuna, Assagao, Siole ani Oxel lokachi Otmik goroz samballtalli. Punn chotter aslimkotche bandkam kelele dekhun ti chodd vorsam ubi urli nam. Atam fokot kalea fatracho Khuris Sonarkhettir assa. 
