==='''Siolechi Igroz'''=== 
Siolechi Igroz 1568 vorsa Gaunsavaddea atam Mae De Deus kopel assa tea zagear bandleli. (Oxem boroup asleli fatorn kopelachea compoundan assa). Hache bandkam kotche asle zait ani ti fokot 32 vorsam ubi urlim. 
1600 vorsam Missionorani ek vhoddli Igroz eka dusrea zagear ji vortotali Siolechea modem ani sogllea lokhak faideachi bandunk eujili. Punn favo te poixe nasle dekhun ti bandunk zateli von am oxem vhodil chintana don Portugez karbari Portugalak- sun ietana eka bhari tufanak sampodle. Tanche kode St. Antonichi murti asli ani  tani agoun keli kit e bondiak bore bashen pautat tea zagear te ek Igroz bandtele.
Tanchi vhodde Chapora dorean bhitor soro dhavea vatten Marna paulli. Hangasor tanchi bhett Franciscan missionarashi zali ani 1630 vorsa Mae De Deus Saibinik bhettoun nhu pun St. Anthonik bhettoun bandli. 



Siolechi Igroz atam Paduache St. Snthonik bhettoilea. Igorjek don tori assat ani ek frontpiece assa tossech Serpentik eke doriek/ razvak bandun hatan asleli Sant Anthonichea murti Igorjechea bandkam korunk di nasli. Lokhani St. Anthoni lagim adar maglo ani St. Anthonichea hatan aslelea razvak farouli. Igorjent murteo, chitram ani Igorjechi ghantir hea murtecho chitr khunaileli assa.
20vea Xekdeache survatek St. Antonichi Igroz ekdom porni zali. Igorjeche pare ani moder anig sarkem korunk zaina zale ani sogli Igroz poddtaxi zali. Firgozkarani teach zagear novi Igroz bandche tharailo.
Hea Igorjechi buniad Novembarache 1902 vorsam ghatli ani Decemberak 28ver 1907 hachi Consecration/ sthapnni zali.

