===Siolechi Kopela ===
====Gaunsavaddeche Mae de Deus Kopel==== 
Gaunsavaddeche Mae de Deus 1847 hea vorsam bandle. Tea adi Kristi lokek Tropache  kopelant Atmik gorzank voitalint. Gaunsavaddeche teg bhav Santa, Ganexa ani zagre Gauns poile Kristanv converts zaun asle. Fr. Cyrico Fernandes (MSFS), Victor Santas, dr. Cosmas ani Fr. Damian Fernandes tanche sonsod zaun asle. Fr. Cyrico Fernandes jivit Brazilak ho pustok “Indian Apostle in Brazil” Rev. Fr. Damian Fernandesan boroila. Hem Kopel Gaunsavaddeachea Holy Cross Conventa mukhar assa. Hea Kopelache Fest Maiache Poilea aitarak zata.
St. Sebastian( Marna)
====St. Sebastian, Marna====
Hem Kopel Marnechea modlea vaddeant assa ani tin vadde: Voilo vaddo,  Modlovaddo, ani Chauddivaddeantlo. He KMopel Prabhu ghoranantle zagear bandla. Fr. Thomas Lobochea adaran Padrik raupak ghor bandle. Fr. Phillip M. D’Souza hea Kopelacho Kopelaum zaun also. Tanne 15 vorsam hanga vaur kelo. Kopelache fest Janerache 20ve uprant aitarak zata. 
====Dongormarg Chapel====
Hanga ek dhaktule, khup porne Povitr Khursache Kopelui mhuntat bandlele assa. Hem Kopel itle uchariek assa ki Arabian Sea sun  disti podta. Ek dhaktule dhove sukne eka khodpar boslelea bhashen dista. Dor vorsa Korezmant xizechea budvarak Katholik lok pursavam vori voitat. Tornattem Jezu bashen ek vhodlo lankdacho khuris khandar geun hea dongrar choddtat.
====Our Lady of Immaculate conception Chapel, Guddem====
Hem kopel Guddemchea lokhachea atmik gorzak faiddeache poddta. Hem kopel 1763 vorsam ube kelele. Decembrache 8 tarker hanga kopelache fest zata..
