===Fatima Saibinnichi vhodd murti===
 
hi saibinnichi murti Mae De Deus kopelachea angnant asa. 8 December 1943 hea vorsa hi murti staploli. Tea velar Fr. Lazarus Andre sokol kopel cholltalem. Purai siolent hea ekuch vaddeant ghora ghoranim Saibinn bhovna . 1943 vorsa hi murti bosovpachem ek karonn mhollear. Sogllea vaddeantlea lokanim ekttai ieun purai October mhoineant saibinichea paim-ia kodde ieun ters korcho ani hantuntlean tancho ekvott anik ghott korcho mhunn tor tea vorsa saun gausoddkaram hi porpompora chalu dovrit aileat.  Dor vorsa 13 october hea vorsa vhodda dobajean Saibinnichi porob monoitat. 

